title: TES V : Skyrim - Secunda Edition
description: TES V: Skyrim - Enhanced Edition is a personal performance-friendly medium-sized Modlist that aims to offer an enhancement of the original graphics and gameplay of Skyrim. Here is the core motivation of this modlist : what we believed to be Skyrim back in 2011, our memories embellished by the nostalgia of this game, are embodied in this Modlist.
author: Heilinger Krest
